    "content": "<em>Ans.</em>&mdash;That is all right; and have those engaged to carry the burden of that work, and not hold the people there [at the camp meeting] to hear those particular things. They have no special work in that branch to do. The time is too precious to be spent in that way.&mdash;<span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"TSS 114.1\" data-link=\"121.465\"><em>Testimonies on Sabbath-School Work</em>, 114</span>.",
